Package: mapfuser
Type: Package
Title: Create Consensus Genetic Maps and Estimate Recombination Rates
Version: 0.1.1
Author: Dennis van Muijen, Ram Kumar Basnet, Nathalie J. Dek
Maintainer: Dennis van Muijen <d.van.muijen@rijkzwaan.nl>
Description: Create consensus genetic maps with LPmerge (see Endelman and Plomion et al.,2014) and model the relationship between genomic and genetic distance using thin-plate regression splines (see Wood et al.,2003). Perform quality control on input data and visualise intermediate steps.
Depends:
    igraph
